WEBVTT

00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:04.325
The Foolproof Method of Reading 1 Read ten pages daily

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:07.287
preferably without interruption but don't try to catch up if

00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:11.725
missed 2 Repeat today's ten pages ten times at least

00:00:11.738 --> 00:00:15.588
five times should be the minimum 3 Limit daily reading

00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:18.925
to no more than ten pages regardless of comprehension memory

00:00:18.950 --> 00:00:23.562
capacity or personal interest Stick to ten pages only it's

00:00:23.575 --> 00:00:25.312
strongly discouraged to binge-read

